{"tid":2435241,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎｜德童書指「病毒來自中國」 被斥埋下仇恨種子 中國總領館嚴正交涉","createTime":"2021-03-06T06:01:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T16:02:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":72,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"6e8663518aa628cfb9e2383956296484c1b89458","tid":2435241,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:01:45.000Z","msg":"德國一本兒童繪本讀物，因在描述武漢肺炎疫情時，表示「這種病毒來自中國，並從那裡向世界傳播」，被德國當地的華人指摘該說法存在誤導，「讓人產生中國製造並傳播了這種病毒的聯想」，同時在德國小孩中埋下仇恨中國的種子。中國駐漢堡總領館日前更發文，表示「高度重視有關動向」，已第一時間向相關出版社提出嚴正交涉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210306/JMBDKHUZM5BBRL4Q3CHCMIIPBQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210306%2FJMBDKHUZM5BBRL4Q3CHCMIIPBQ%2F&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=49bff29c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210306%2FJMBDKHUZM5BBRL4Q3CHCMIIPBQ%2F&h=38d354e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210306/JMBDKHUZM5BBRL4Q3CHCMIIPBQ/</a>"},{"pid":"a6847a9fb65a2c74340d3070d7655a9e5e7c4626","tid":2435241,"uid":51271,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:05:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">中國武漢肺炎</span>"},{"pid":"cd7de8d3bf2ee2a6fee1bb00ec8aff63976c4d5b","tid":2435241,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:11:01.000Z","msg":"來自美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8fc476bcc6c3819d166858f8ab1b379b5691ed2","tid":2435241,"uid":128261,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"支那肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bec9f83f7dc9e982b61c3accf3a79beedc145fb","tid":2435241,"uid":40272,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:14:48.000Z","msg":"國安法拉柒佢"},{"pid":"3250ad